comment: [Incidental or immaterial] Garnett (MIN) and Randolph (MEM) make incidental contact with one another as they try to establish post position.
Green (MEM) makes contact to LaVine's (MIN) body as he drives toward the basket.
Miller (MIN) does not obtain a legal guarding position and affects Conley's (MEM) RSBQ on the perimeter.
Green (MEM) sets the screen on Miller (MIN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Wiggins (MIN) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Conley's (MEM) body that affects his jump shot.
Miller (MIN) commits a take foul on Randolph (MEM).
[Incidental or immaterial] Green (MEM) makes incidental contact with LaVine (MIN) that does not affect his ability to retrieve the loose ball.
Towns (MIN) commits a take foul on Green (MEM).
Towns (MIN) makes a legal move in the post with Gasol (MEM) defending him.
Towns (MIN) commits a take foul on Chalmers (MEM).
Towns (MIN) sets the screen on Green (MEM) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gasol (MEM) makes contact with LaVine's (MIN) body and arms that affects his layup attempt.
LaVine (MIN) commits a take foul on Chalmers (MEM).
Bjelica (MIN) commits a take foul on Green (MEM).
Bjelica (MIN) commits a take foul on Chalmers (MEM).
Chalmers (MEM) is in legal guarding position defending the jump shot by LaVine (MIN).
